# Sepolia Testnet Configuration
SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=https://sepolia.infura.io/v3/YOUR_INFURA_PROJECT_ID
PRIVATE_KEY=your_private_key_here
ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=your_etherscan_api_key_here

# Alternative RPC providers:
# ALCHEMY_SEPOLIA_URL=https://eth-sepolia.g.alchemy.com/v2/YOUR_ALCHEMY_KEY
# PUBLIC_SEPOLIA_RPC=https://rpc.sepolia.org

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env
# 2. Replace YOUR_INFURA_PROJECT_ID with your Infura project ID (free tier available)
# 3. Replace your_private_key_here with your MetaMask private key
# 4. Replace your_etherscan_api_key_here with your Etherscan API key (free tier available)
# 5. Never commit .env file to version control

# Getting required services:
# - Infura: https://infura.io (free tier: 100k requests/month)
# - MetaMask: Export private key from MetaMask settings
# - Etherscan: https://etherscan.io/apis (free tier: 5 requests/second)
